Start the redirect server

Usage:
  redirectly [CONFIG --port PORT --reload]
  redirectly --init
  redirectly -h | --help | --version

Options:
  -p --port PORT
    Listening port [default: 3000]

  -i --init
    Create a sample config file and exit

  -r --reload
    Read the INI file with every request

  -h --help
    Show this help

  --version
    Show version number

Parameters:
  CONFIG
    Path to config file [default: redirects.ini]

Environment Variables:
  REDIRECTLY_RELOAD
    Set to a non empty value in order to read the INI file with every request
    (same as --reload)

Examples:
  redirectly --init
  redirectly config.ini --port 4000 --reload
